<div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] p-8 rounded-lg">
  <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-1 uppercase">Request Estimate</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">The No-Surprise Guarantee</p>
  
  <form class="space-y-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <input type="text" placeholder="FULL NAME*" class="w-full bg-black border border-gray-800 text-white p-3 text-xs placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#f57f20]" />
      <input type="tel" placeholder="PHONE NUMBER*" class="w-full bg-black border border-gray-800 text-white p-3 text-xs placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#f57f20]" />
    </div>
    
    <input type="email" placeholder="EMAIL ADDRESS*" class="w-full bg-black border border-gray-800 text-white p-3 text-xs placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#f57f20]" />
    
    <textarea placeholder="PROPERTY ADDRESS (START TYPING)*" rows="3" class="w-full bg-black border border-gray-800 text-white p-3 text-xs placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#f57f20]"></textarea>
    
    <div class="flex items-start space-x-2 mt-4">
      <input type="checkbox" id="terms" class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 bg-black border-gray-800 rounded focus:ring-0 text-[#f57f20]" />
      <label for="terms" class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 leading-tight">
        BY CHECKING THIS BOX, I AGREE TO DECK MASTERS' <a href="#" class="text-[#f57f20]">TERMS & PRIVACY POLICY</a>. AND CONSENT TO RECEIVE SMS MESSAGES ABOUT MY PROJECT. MSG & DATA RATES MAY APPLY. REPLY STOP TO OPT OUT.*
      </label>
    </div>
    
     <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
      <input type="checkbox" id="marketing" class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 bg-black border-gray-800 rounded focus:ring-0 text-[#f57f20]" />
      <label for="marketing" class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 leading-tight">
        CONSENT: I AGREE TO RECEIVING AUTOMATED MARKETING TEXTS OR CALLS FROM OR ON BEHALF OF DECK MASTERS AT THE NUMBER PROVIDED. CONSENT IS NOT A CONDITION OF PURCHASE. MSG FREQUENCY VARIES. MSG & DATA RATES MAY APPLY. REPLY STOP TO CANCEL.*
      </label>
    </div>

    <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-[#f57f20] hover:bg-[#d96a17] text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded mt-4 text-xs uppercase transition-colors">
      Check Availability & Get Quote â†’
    </button>
  </form>

  <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-800">
    <p class="text-white italic text-sm mb-2">"From the initial consultation to the final product... Jordan gave us great recommendations."</p>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase">- Anton Szender</p>
  </div>
</div>
